    <div class="text-3xl font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-5">

    <!-- NODES.GARDEN -->
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Technical Founder"
      subtitle="May 2024 – Dec 2025 — nodes.garden (remote)"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-2 grid gap-2">
        <li>Founded and led the technical development of a Node-as-a-Service SaaS platform built with Ruby on Rails.</li>
        <li>Owned backend architecture, core domain modeling, APIs, background processing, and internal tooling.</li>
        <li>Built systems orchestrating operations across thousands of servers via API.</li>
        <li>Scaled the platform from 0 to 16,000+ users without external engineering resources.</li>
        <li>Implemented subscription billing, payments, dashboards, and operational workflows.</li>
        <li>Completed Techstars Web3 2025, XFounders Season 4 and Founder.University Cohort 9 programs.</li>
      </ul>
      <span class="text-sm font-light">
        Tech: Ruby on Rails, PostgreSQL, GoodJob, Hotwire, TailwindCSS, RSpec, Docker, fly.io
      </span>
    </TimeLineElement>

    <!-- REINVENTED HOSPITALITY -->
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Ruby Engineer"
      subtitle="Sep 2024 – Mar 2025 — reinvented-hospitality.com (remote, time-based contract)"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-2 grid gap-2">
        <li>Successfully launched a production POS system used in hotel and restaurant operations.</li>
        <li>Built core features for hotel and restaurant management workflows.</li>
        <li>Delivered reporting, exports, and operational tooling.</li>
      </ul>
      <span class="text-sm font-light">
        Tech: Ruby on Rails, PostgreSQL, Sidekiq, Hotwire, Docker
      </span>
    </TimeLineElement>

    <!-- XOMETRY -->
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Ruby Engineer"
      subtitle="Oct 2022 – Sep 2024 — xometry.de (remote)"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-2 grid gap-2">
        <li>Worked on a large-scale manufacturing marketplace connecting hundreds of thousands of buyers & suppliers globally.</li>
        <li>Successfully launched UK and TR regional apps under tight deadlines.</li>
        <li>Designed and implemented async intercompany communication systems.</li>
        <li>Built foundational domain systems (HS codes, manufacturing attributes, pricing logic).</li>
        <li>Architectured and executed migration of the multi-repo architecture into a unified platform.</li>
        <li>Worked extensively with PostgreSQL: query optimization, indexes, data modeling.</li>
      </ul>
