      </span>
    </TimeLineElement>

    <!-- EARLIER EXPERIENCE -->
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Ruby Engineer"
      subtitle="2019 – 2021 at sputnik8.com, igooods.ru, rubyroidlabs.com"
    >
      Backend development across e-commerce, travel, insurance, and internal tooling products. Both in-house and outsourcing projects from EU/US.
      <br>
      <span class="text-sm font-light">
        Tech: Ruby on Rails, PostgreSQL, Sidekiq, APIs, Payments
      </span>
    </TimeLineElement>

